OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FQuite cloudy but some bright or
OL,6,Fsunny intervals in north along with a
OL,7,Ffew showers which could turn heavy and
OL,8,Fthundery in the far north. More
OL,9,Fpersistent rain developing across
OL,10,FLochaber and extending north later.
OL,11,FMostly light winds.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FMostly cloudy with occasional
OL,14,Fbursts of showery rain, with just a
OL,15,Ffew clearer interludes, Perhaps some
OL,16,Fcoastal haar over Caithness and
OL,17,FSutherland.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
