OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FAnother day of bright spells
OL,6,Fand scattered showers, some of these
OL,7,Fturning out quite heavy especially
OL,8,Fover East Highland.
OL,9,
OL,10,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FBrighter
OL,11,Fwith sunny intervals and a few showers
OL,12,Fon Friday. Rain spreading from west on
OL,13,FSaturday, turning heavy in west. Then
OL,14,Fback to sunshine and showers on Sunday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
